 Freer - Parliamentary Under Secretary of State","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"8ff7dcfb-ad6f-4332-8114-8a1a50921951","details":{"current":false,"ended_on":"2022-07-08T00:00:00+01:00","person_appointment_order":7147,"started_on":"2021-09-17T00:00:00+01:00"},"document_type":"role_appointment","links":{"person":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/people/mike-freer","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/people/mike-freer","base_path":"/government/people/mike-freer","content_id":"4202c431-908f-4029-a26c-b5fa267231eb","details":{"body":"<p>Mike Freer was Parliamentary Under Secretary of State for the Ministry of Justice between 20 September 2022 and 5 July 2024.</p>\n\n<p>He was Minister for Exports and Minister for Equalities between September 2021 and 6 July 2022.</p>\n\n<p>He was a Member of Parliament for Finchley and Golders Green from 2010 to 2024. Mike was Assistant Government Whip between June 2017 and July 2018. He was also Lord Commissioner of the Treasury from July 2018 to December 2019 and served as Comptroller of HM Household from December 2019 to September 2021.</p>\n","image":{"alt_text":"Mike Freer","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/614c2d9b8fa8f561075cadcd/s465_Mike-Freer.jpg"}},"document_type":"person","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-07-18T10:27:48Z","schema_name":"person","title":"Mike Freer","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/mike-freer","withdrawn":false}],"role":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/ministers/parliamentary-under-secretary-of-state-minister-for-exports","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/ministers/parliamentary-under-secretary-of-state-minister-for-exports","base_path":"/government/ministers/parliamentary-under-secretary-of-state-minister-for-exports","content_id":"b5962ae6-bbf1-4cf6-9350-ec85e4e16122","details":{"body":"<p>Responsibilities include:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>local growth</li>\n  <li>small businesses</li>\n  <li>Post Office</li>\n  <li>